The paper discusses an algorithm for minimizing the difference between two submodular functions, which is relevant to several commonly used metrics in machine learning, such as mutual information and conditional mutual information. Therefore, the paper is likely to belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), data structures and algorithms (cs.DS), information theory (cs.IT), and social and information networks (cs.SI).
